              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Term life:</strong> CHF 50-200/month for CHF 500K-1M coverage</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Whole life:</strong> CHF 200-800+/month for CHF 500K coverage</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Professional needs:</strong> CHF 500K-2M+ typical coverage range</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Coverage calculation:</strong> 5-10x annual income + debt + education costs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
