          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Term life insurance is usually optimal for professionals: 5-10x higher death benefit for same premium cost. Use savings to maximize 3rd pillar contributions (better tax benefits and returns). Choose whole life only for estate planning, business succession, or if you've maxed other tax-advantaged accounts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

